shadow-13vm9: CMD: shadow-13vm9.shadow.whamcloud.com lctl get_param -n at_max
error on LL_IOC_LMV_SETSTRIPE &apos;/mnt/lustre/d70d.replay-single/test1&apos; (3): stripe already set
error: mkdir: create stripe dir &apos;/mnt/lustre/d70d.replay-single/test1&apos; failed
mkdir fails
shadow-13vm10: mdc.lustre-MDT0000-mdc-*.mds_server_uuid in FULL state after 15 sec
shadow-13vm9: mdc.lustre-MDT0000-mdc-*.mds_server_uuid in FULL state after 15 sec
/usr/lib64/lustre/tests/replay-single.sh: line 2114: kill: (16746) - No such process
